---
title: Smart Ground Turkey Parmesan-Style Patties with Veggie Medley and Potatoes
description: Featuring ground turkey patties smothered in marinara sauce and ooey-gooey melted cheese, this dinner offers all the comforts of classic turkey Parmesan. For your sides, potatoes, peppers and zucchini are roasted and then finished with Parmesan and parsley. Talk about hearty and satisfying!
